90
00:06:19,431 --> 00:06:25,232
And I feel like it's a good time to step away and give other people an opportunity to get involved.

91
00:06:27,193 --> 00:06:29,637
you know, provide leadership for the city.

92
00:06:30,679 --> 00:06:38,373
And I do, about a year ago, I joined the board of Bike to the Sea, which is the organization that

93
00:06:40,118 --> 00:06:43,983
is kind of the stewards of the Northern Strand Trail.

94
00:06:44,885 --> 00:06:56,580
And actually just this morning, I rode out to Saugus in the rain and attended the official ribbon cutting

95
00:06:57,241 --> 00:06:59,082
that opens the trail.

96
00:06:59,102 --> 00:07:02,624
It's actually been complete for about a year.

97
00:07:04,025 --> 00:07:13,729
But the Secretary of Environmental Affairs was there, mayors from all the five towns that it goes through.

98
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:17,511
So that was kind of a big moment.

99
00:07:19,032 --> 00:07:21,993
And so I'm doing, I'm doing lots of things over there.

100
00:07:22,733 --> 00:07:30,236
