205
00:15:23,568 --> 00:15:26,070
This is what the road looks like.

206
00:15:32,494 --> 00:15:37,517
So you can see there's kind of a long stretch here where there's not a lot of crosswalks.

207
00:15:39,238 --> 00:15:43,962
